                        <additions>
                            <list>
                                 <item xml:id="a1">
                                     <desc type="GuestText">
                                         <locus target="#1r"/>
                                        Beginning of a text in honour of the archangel <persName ref="PRS8065Raguel">Rāguʾel</persName> containing <foreign xml:lang="gez">ʾasmāt</foreign>.
                                        The text ends up abruptly. The first line is preceded by an almost completely illegible line in red ink.
                                        Some letters are illegible due to the ink, the handwriting and the state of preservation of the leaf.
                                        The entire text is the following:
                                    <q xml:lang="gez">
                                        ድርሳን፡ ዘቅዱስ፡ ራጉኤል፡ ብሃ<gap reason="illegible" unit="chars" quantity="2"/>መብሕኤል፡
                                        በዕትናኤል፡ <add place="above">በ</add>ሃድናኤል፡ <gap reason="illegible" unit="chars" quantity="1"/>ጽሐድኤል፡ እሎንተ፡ ቃላት፡
                                        ዘነገሮ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ዘቅዱስ፡ ራጉኤል፡ ብሑር፡ ዘቅዱስ።
                                    </q>
                                     </desc>
                                </item>

                                <item xml:id="a2">
                                    <desc type="GuestText">
                                        <title type="incomplete" ref="LIT5086MagicPrayer"/>
                                        <locus from="1v" to="2v"/>
                                        Protective prayer against the hail, written in the same hand of <ref target="#a1">the previous note</ref>.
                                        The text begins on  <locus target="#2r"/> (<q><seg part="I">ጸሎተ፡ በረድ፡ <gap reason="illegible" unit="chars" quantity="1"/>ብርድ፡ አስተባርድ፡ ድኵል፡ ተከልከል፡ ሽር፡
                                            <gap reason="illegible" unit="chars" quantity="1"/>እሰ<gap reason="illegible" unit="chars" quantity="2"/>ታለ፡
                                            እግዚአብሔር፡ ዘገብረ፡ ሰማየ፡ ወመድረ፡ ኢታውርድ፡ <sic>በርድ፡</sic>
                                        </seg></q>), then continues on <locus target="#2v"/>, and terminates possibly abruptly on <locus target="#1v"/>
                                        (<q><seg part="F">ተማኅፀንኩ፡ በሚካኤል፡ ወገብርኤል፡ በማርያም፡ ድንግል፡ ወላዲተ፡ አምላክ፡ ቀዳሚሁ፡ ቃል፡ <gap reason="illegible" unit="chars" quantity="10"/>ንያ፡</seg></q>).
                                    </desc>
                                </item>


